cowrat.recoled.audio
Class Profile

java.lang.Object
  cowrat.recoled.audio.Profile
Deprecated. These JMF-based classes have been dropped in favour of our own implementations. Use cowrat.recplaj.recorder.Recorder for audio recording and cowrat.rexplore.hnm.MakeHanmerProfile for activity logging (post-processing) instead. THIS PACKAGE IS NO LONGER USED IN RECOLED AND WILL SOON BE REMOVED.

public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object

Store an array of active profiles, one for each participant: 'Activity Profiles' are vectors of booleans representing whether a stream was active or not over a period of time.

See Also:
cowrat.recplaj.recorder.Recorder, cowrat.rexplor.hnm.MakeHanmerProfile
